              "english": "On one hand, technology is useful, on the other hand, it affects society"
            }
          ],
          "common_mistakes": [
            "Use this structure for balanced, nuanced arguments"
          ]
        },
        {
          "rule": "Expressing Strong Opinions",
          "explanation": "Use 'ana 9tnna3 blli' (I'm convinced that), 'ma kayn tta shkk' (there's no doubt), 'wad7 blli' (it's clear that).",
          "examples": [
            {
              "arabic": "أنا قتنعت بلي التعليم هو الحل",
